The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Dalmiya taking legal opinion

A STAFF REPORTER

 BCCI Hearing 

Calcutta: Former BCCI president Jagmohan Dalmiya is taking legal opinion on whether to attend the BCCI disciplinary committee hearing on Sunday. 

He is consulting his lawyers on the summons issued by the committee, a source said on Wednesday. The hearing is related to alleged misappropriation of Pilcom funds. 




